```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many washcloths are stacked on top of each other?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many washcloths are stacked on top of each other?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} >= 4 or {ANSWER1} >= 4')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
